>{}</li></ul>"},"tha-ap315:0.3":{"pli":"Gatasaññakattheraapadāna ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"tha-ap315:1.1":{"pli":"“Ākāseva padaṁ natthi, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:1.2":{"pli":"ambare anilañjase; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:1.3":{"pli":"Siddhatthaṁ jinamaddakkhiṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:1.4":{"pli":"gacchantaṁ tidivaṅgaṇe. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap315:2.1":{"pli":"Anileneritaṁ disvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:2.2":{"pli":"sammāsambuddhacīvaraṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:2.3":{"pli":"Vitti mamāhu tāvade, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:2.4":{"pli":"disvāna gamanaṁ muniṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap315:3.1":{"pli":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:3.2":{"pli":"yaṁ saññamalabhiṁ tadā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:3.3":{"pli":"Duggatiṁ nābhijānāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:3.4":{"pli":"buddhasaññāyidaṁ phalaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap315:4.1":{"pli":"Paṭisambhidā catasso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:4.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap315:4.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"tha-ap315:5.1":{"pli":"Itthaṁ sudaṁ āyasmā gatasaññako thero imā gāthāyo abhāsitthāti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"tha-ap315:6.1":{"pli":"Gatasaññakattherassāpadānaṁ tatiyaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}}}